review: Hi, First of all a big thanks to Sankari Mam, Divya Mam and to the whole staff for being so good to me. Sankari mam made me so comfortable. She told me not to be discouraged and boosted me with lot of confidence. Few doctors only spend this much amount of time. I felt very positive after meeting her.Very amazed to see the negative reviews, asking for lot of money  and all, which according to me is not at all true because the fertility medicines usually cost very high also the doctor told me to follow step by step procedure. Had she be like this she could have jumped to a big list of tests followed by numerous high cost procedure. Thank you to everyone once again. Hoping and pray for the best

Being informed many times it’s only for consulting.. they had billed 4750 ******* ******* . Post receiving bill found that she has already prescribed medicine separately for the issue and all the bills for future scope and understand if there is future scope for problem.. total bill was 6350 for just consulting and few medicines for just general query and issue

*** ************ ** **** ****** ****** ** **** ****** ***** 
(I do not ve any doubt about her caliber, yet). I was going to her since the first month, i conceived. We took scan every time, though the growth was normal. She promised for a normal delivery as the growth and conditions seemed to be normal. But on the last day, when i had pain, we informed her in the evening (5'o clock) about it and she said she'll be at the hospital.First, We went there and waited and waited, the lady did not turn up. Staffs cooked up new stories for her not showing up (some said that she is not well and some said she is at trichy). Why the hell would she ask to come if she cannot handle..  Second, there were no doctors for an hour and finally one assistant Dr came and she said we need to operate immediately... otherwise, it is hard... We agreed. After some time, failing to make arrangements asap, she said "can we wait and try for normal" as they did not have paediatrician, anaesthetists, gyny, even enough nurses at that time... And, they operated only next day morning, that too without Dr.Samundishankari... The funniest thing is that i don't know who did the surgery for me... This 12 hour delayed surgery is supposed to affect my baby's brain and facing several problems *** ******* ** *** ************ *** ******************* 
Another biggest mistake was a careless injury on baby's head during surgery.. Even after paying sooo much, me and my baby were not guarenteed proper treatment / care... ***** ** ********* *** *** ******** ******** *** *********** I've written elaborately so that nobody else should get affected like me...

context: Fertilisation In Vitro - Embryo Transfer (IVF - ET),
review:
I recommend for the people who don't mind spending lot because everything is costly here. In the first visit itself they gave big list for test which cost you around 10 k and prescribed medicine cost to around 3k . For the further process they charge according to your problem. For me they suggested following process.

Step 1. Scan for the formation for the egg :- 1.5 k (this process to be repeated for 3 times) . This helps to see the egg growth and if we have relationship at that time there is a 10 % chances for pregnancy.

Step 2. IUI Treatment :- 4.5 k (this process to be repeated for 3 times). This has 30 % chances of pregnancy.

Step 3. (From this their game starts) Mini or green IVF Treatment :- 95 k this has to be repetitions various person to person. Max they this will repeated 3 times. Success rate 20 %

Step 4. Traditional IVF :- 1.95 Lakhs Max this will repeated 3 times. Success rate 50 %.

Step 5. ICSI :- 3 Lakhs and above this will repeated 3 times. Success rate 50  - 60%.

In the above treatment maximum 80 % will get pregnant if not your hard earned money lost.


Apart from the above points the test & scan which your doing with them they just write in piece of paper. They don't give in the professional way.


Final Verdict :- This is hospital is not for the middle class people. People who don't mind spending then definitely this is your cup of tea. 
'

I never seen irresponsible Doctor like her.. She might be very experienced .when she don't have to check the patient. *** ***** **** *** ** ****** My appointment time is 12.30pm . Doctor came to hospital by 3.30pm and her assistant took the history and mentioned some medicine for my problem.. Meanwhile Doctor was very busy taking to her colleague about Some discount offers in some shops. The assistant told Doctor about my problem ..that Doctor didn't have to listen and said ok ask the patient to do all the checkups including scanning and blood test . And ask the patient to come after 1week ..this was the reply given by Doctor ..I felt really bad ... That shrusti hospital charged me 950rs for registration and Doctor consultation fee..  It's really worst spending my 3hrs time and money with Doctor and that hospital .. I strongly recommend people not to waste their money by vising this Doctor.

The doctors are friendly, they diagnosed and treated the problem systematically explaining the line of treatment to be followed. The treatment was effective which further enhanced the faith in the doctors here . also the supporting staff is very cordial and helping. I recommend this clinic/hospital .
